**

20:50.016 --> 20:52.985
Crazy Eddie's
having a pillow sale!

20:53.052 --> 20:54.821
Every pillow you can see...

20:54.887 --> 20:58.625
Big pillows, large pillows,
throw pillows, every pillow!

20:58.691 --> 21:00.927
And it's only
for this special month!

21:00.993 --> 21:02.028
Oh!

21:05.732 --> 21:08.167
Call a guy and tell him
something gross.

21:08.234 --> 21:09.736
Ew. Never.
I'll take a zit sticker.

21:09.802 --> 21:11.471
I knew
you'd still be here!

21:11.538 --> 21:13.205
Erica! You came home
to see me!

21:13.272 --> 21:15.908
No, I came home
to fight you all
for invading my privacy!

21:15.975 --> 21:17.444
But Barry said
you were fine with it.

21:17.510 --> 21:19.346
That is
not what I said, Erica.

21:19.412 --> 21:21.781
What I told them was...
Run, JTP!

21:21.848 --> 21:22.849
ALL: JTP!

21:24.050 --> 21:25.485
Okay, I get you're mad,

21:25.552 --> 21:27.554
but can I at least get a kiss
before you flip out?

21:27.620 --> 21:29.288
Yeah, I'm going
back to school.

21:29.356 --> 21:30.723
Wait. That's not...
But I didn't...
